{
  "stem": "3973.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Normally, when they shot people over there, they had to get undressed, put the clothing in a pile.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then the one guy usually, or two, would just sit on the edge of the ravine, like, swinging his feet, and the people would go back, kneel in front of him with the back of the neck.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he would shoot them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Two people pick them up in the pile, and the next guy will go off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this is how the execution was taken place, one at a time, with a pistol shot in the neck.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "These people were shot dressed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And somehow we were grabbed, me and friends of mine, to take the clothing down to the-- what do you call it, where they kept the [INAUDIBLE], this is the clothing barrack, in a wheel barrow.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I remember I went down to this ditch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We went down together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The-- the-- the people were undressed, stacked like wood-- like cords of wood, you know, like going across each other, head to feet, and so on.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I remember this was-- there was one of the people I just saw on side of them was a woman.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was always stuck in my mind, this is the first time I saw a naked woman was a bloodied body.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Anyway, we went down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But as we were going down, there was the wheelbarrows full of clothing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We went searching through them to see if there's anything there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we found a piece of white bread with butter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But it was all bloody.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So I remember we carefully picked the blood away and had a feast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we sat-- you know, they're not the big stories, but somehow, some of these things stick.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
